 "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1374247: Remove the XBL children matching hack, and assert against it. r=xidorn,francois\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 9Q9WpJFczxc\n", "files": ["layout/reftests/dom/reftest.list", "layout/reftests/dom/xbl-children-1.xhtml", "layout/style/nsCSSRuleProcessor.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5c4cb77d75e5848fbbcf191d78b9110274f26761", "parents": ["fe14831a814b7d9d8179d2f838925c1b86452477"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1374247: Keep the hack working on late beta and release, so we can land this a little earlier. r=bz,xidorn\n\nAs Xidorn mentions, if the plan is stylo-in-chrome for 59, we really should land\nthis assertion pretty much now. This ensures that we don't ship 58 without this\nhack.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: JXol2r3BMtC\n", "files": ["layout/style/nsCSSRuleProcessor.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9edca0017ec435f03f3550f6277390d514a7b2d4", "parents": ["5c4cb77d75e5848fbbcf191d78b9110274f26761"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Attila Craciun \u003cacraciun@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out 5 changesets (bug 1413166) for failing valgrind-test at Conditional jump or move depends on uninitialised value(s) at nsCSSRuleProcessor::InitSystemMetrics / InitSystemMetrics / nsCSSRuleProcessor::HasSystemMetric / GetSystemMetric r=backout on a CLOSED TREE.\n\nBacked out changeset b39bf4bf8127 (bug 1413166)\nBacked out changeset e1ef2adcc815 (bug 1413166)\nBacked out changeset 16fd21f5ad8c (bug 1413166)\nBacked out changeset 9e5f5924dad8 (bug 1413166)\nBacked out changeset 3b8671ab0719 (bug 1413166)", "files": ["dom/base/nsGkAtomList.h", "layout/style/nsCSSRuleProcessor.cpp", "layout/style/nsMediaFeatures.cpp", "layout/style/test/chrome/bug418986-2.js", "layout/style/test/test_media_queries.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [nul