e \u003cimg\u003e.  r=bz\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 7afxM9sWmiA", "files": ["dom/base/nsIContentInlines.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "82f3de55cfdf597656fc696c95ef9fab21cd6ce6", "parents": ["9d35e52771e022849cbf6a24d67087bee7c4c827"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mats Palmgren \u003cmats@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1400618 part 4 - Destroy frames before calling nsXBLBinding::ChangeDocument in a few places.  r=bz\n\n\nnsXBLBinding::ChangeDocument calls UnbindAnonymousContent\nwhich calls UnbindFromTree on the content so any frames must be\ndestroyed before that to maintain the invariant that frames are\ndestroyed before unbinding.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 8Icj7zqpuZS", "files": ["dom/xbl/nsBindingManager.cpp", "dom/xml/nsXMLPrettyPrinter.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "fc5b7c39dd167042591c756e94f458c8605ffeea", "parents": ["82f3de55cfdf597656fc696c95ef9fab21cd6ce6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mats Palmgren \u003cmats@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1400618 part 5 - Destroy the frames before removing the AccessibleCaret anonymous content (to ensure it happens before the UnbindFromTree).  r=bz\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Kvudz7bJFEZ", "files": ["layout/base/AccessibleCaret.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "14c27d1d3d54bea1e78a706e3c3fd9a1a699a5cf", "parents": ["fc5b7c39dd167042591c756e94f458c8605ffeea"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mats Palmgren \u003cmats@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1400618 part 6 - Remove the workaround for the broken IsPrimaryFrame() in nsFrame::DestroyFrom since it now works also for NAC frames.  r=bz\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1DFyWZBpzwP", "files": ["layout/generic/nsFrame.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "98a34f65811942ddd47f28ea047d8542c35eea16", "parents": ["14c27d1d3d54bea1e78a706e3c3fd9a1a699a5cf"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jonathan Kew \u003cjkew@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1412090 - patch 1 - Wrap the font family record used to pass font info from chrome to content on macOS in a union, in preparation for using the same mechanism with a different type of font record on Linux. (No functional change here, just the added union type and some renamings from 'font family list' to 'font list' to be more generic.) r=lsalzman", "files": ["dom/ipc/ContentChild.cpp", "dom/ipc/ContentChild.h", "dom/ipc/ContentParent.cpp", "dom/ipc/PContent.ipdl", "gfx/thebes/gfxMacPlatformFontList.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxMacPlatformFontList.mm", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatform.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformMac.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformMac.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c6ad01bf0b669096565646e8f47bb8e6286d22a1", "parents": ["98a34f65811942ddd47f28ea047d8542c35eea16"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jonathan Kew \u003cjkew@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1412090 - patch 2 - Rework the fontconfig-based platform font list implementation to pass the list of available font patterns from chrome to content, instead of letting the content process get it directly from fontconfig. r=lsalzman", "files": ["dom/ipc/ContentChild.cpp", "dom/ipc/ContentChild.h", "dom/ipc/ContentParent.cpp", "dom/ipc/ContentParent.h", "dom/ipc/PContent.ipdl", "gfx/thebes/gfxFcPlatformFontList.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxFcPlatformFontList.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxMacPlatformFontList.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxMacPlatformFontList.mm", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatform.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformGtk.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformGtk.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformMac.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformMac.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bf35d13e27f392dc5dcdab3e7755c69b632f46ab", "parents": ["c6ad01bf0b669096565646e8f47bb8e6286d22a1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jonathan Kew \u003cjkew@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1412090 - patch 3 - Check the sandbox policy to verify font files will be readable by the content process before including them in the system font list. r=gps", "files": ["gfx/thebes/gfxFcPlatformFontList.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxFcPlatformFontList.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a1c1fe33a052ac9ff96fbbe389f53687d25e2afc", "parents": ["bf35d13e27f392dc5dcdab3e7755c69b632f46ab"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jonathan Kew \u003cjkew@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1412090 - patch 4 - Also adopt the ContentParent::NotifyUpdatedFonts method on macOS, so that only the parent process needs to register with CFNotificationCenter for font-changed notifications. r=lsalzman", "files": ["gfx/thebes/gfxMacPlatformFontList.mm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f9763adebe6847072575978df2f8e010d790b083", "parents": ["a1c1fe33a052ac9ff96fbbe389f53687d25e2afc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jonathan Kew \u003cjkew@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out csets f9763adebe68, a1c1fe33a052, bf35d13e27f3, c6ad01bf0b66 (bug 1412090) for ASan failures.", "files": ["dom/ipc/ContentChild.cpp", "dom/ipc/ContentChild.h", "dom/ipc/ContentParent.cpp", "dom/ipc/ContentParent.h", "dom/ipc/PContent.ipdl", "gfx/thebes/gfxFcPlatformFontList.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxFcPlatformFontList.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxMacPlatformFontList.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxMacPlatformFontList.mm", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatform.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformGtk.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformGtk.h", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformMac.cpp", "gfx/thebes/gfxPlatformMac.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "df53224b917158a08bccadeef488f30a2b2ac89b", "parents": ["f9763adebe6847072575978df2f8e010d790b083"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Sebastian Hengst \u003carchaeopteryx@coole-files.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out 6 changesets (bug 1400618) for asserting in clipboard's dom/browser-element/mochitest/test_browserElement_inproc_CopyPaste.html on Windows 7 debug without e10s. r=backout\n\nBacked out changeset 98a34f658119 (bug 1400618)\nBacked out changeset 14c27d1d3d54 (bug 1400618)\nBacked out changeset fc5b7c