]}, {"author": "Mats Palmgren \u003cmats@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1400618 part 4 - Destroy frames before calling nsXBLBinding::ChangeDocument in a few places.  r=bz\n\n\nnsXBLBinding::ChangeDocument calls UnbindAnonymousContent\nwhich calls UnbindFromTree on the content so any frames must be\ndestroyed before that to maintain the invariant that frames are\ndestroyed before unbinding.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 8Icj7zqpuZS", "files": ["dom/xbl/nsBindingManager.cpp", "dom/xml/nsXMLPrettyPrinter.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "82659642e0583a8e493bea4f0a7bfb75dc48accd", "parents": ["50c2aba68909c45c8136fd5ba20865e9c0309b87"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mats Palmgren \u003cmats@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1400618 part 5 - Destroy the frames before removing the AccessibleCaret anonymous content (to ensure it happens before the UnbindFromTree).  r=bz\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Kvudz7bJFEZ", "files": ["layout/base/AccessibleCaret.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e46bd0b42454a446bd1080a4d32f92386d2d2336", "parents": ["82659642e0583a8e493bea4f0a7bfb75dc48accd"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mats Palmgren \u003cmats@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1400618 part 6 - Remove the workaround for the broken IsPrimaryFrame() in nsFrame::DestroyFrom since it now works also for NAC frames.  r=bz\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 1DFyWZBpzwP", "files": ["layout/generic/nsFrame.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cd9f14f9ea6d4bcd175874352c402613503a86d8", "parents": ["e46bd0b42454a446bd1080a4d32f92386d2d2336"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Henning \u003cjh+bugzilla@buttercookie.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1414838 - Show stop button again as soon as page loading starts. r=nechen\n\nAs of bug 1366672, case START no longer falls through in order to allow for a\ndifferent behaviour of the progress indicator, however we still need to add\nUpdateFlags.PRO