tializer. r=jandem\n\nOn Darwin this would cause a race between two static initializers.", "files": ["js/src/shell/js.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "af56f51a55b1492f2fc22b2bf3a61cf69cc89d57", "parents": ["1413e5b916a34fba9f3b4db7e2812ed52ccc89da"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Lee Salzman \u003clsalzman@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1412545 - avoid race condition when setting Cairo ft font user data. r=jrmuizel\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4aqfj2xlCc2", "files": ["gfx/2d/ScaledFontFontconfig.cpp", "gfx/webrender_bindings/Moz2DImageRenderer.cpp", "gfx/webrender_bindings/moz.build"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b80f6e02f7571660442822b2c8800a6031a609f7", "parents": ["af56f51a55b1492f2fc22b2bf3a61cf69cc89d57"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrea Marchesini \u003camarchesini@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1415086 - Fixing a out-of-scope issue for a string in Worklet code, r=qdot", "files": ["dom/worklet/Worklet.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1c6eac3c74d516b2e76ebee8b07a663341133fda", "parents": ["b80f6e02f7571660442822b2c8800a6031a609f7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Georg Fritzsche \u003cgeorg.fritzsche@googlemail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1408975 - Allow to register new addon events for an existing category. r=dexter", "files": ["toolkit/components/telemetry/TelemetryEvent.cpp", "toolkit/components/telemetry/docs/collection/events.rst", "toolkit/components/telemetry/tests/unit/test_TelemetryEvents.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "82a3eab8a078e2d7d17817c47ae3c417928554e5", "parents": ["1c6eac3c74d516b2e76ebee8b07a663341133fda"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Georg Fritzsche \u003cgeorg.fritzsche@googlemail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1414638 - Remove expiry_date property for Telemetry events. r=dexter", "files": ["toolkit/components/telemetry/EventInfo.h", "toolkit/components/telemetry/Events.yaml", "toolkit/co