, add site-specific permissions to prevent pages from overriding keyboard shortcuts. This is done by preventing the key combination from being sent to the content page, r=felipe\n\nUsers can block the overriding of shortcuts using the permissions tab of the page info dialog, as with other permissions. Site permissions also allows the use of permissions.default.shortcuts to block overriding shortcuts for all sites.", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/permissions/browser_permissions.js", "browser/base/content/test/permissions/browser_reservedkey.js", "browser/base/content/test/permissions/permissions.html", "browser/locales/en-US/chrome/browser/sitePermissions.properties", "browser/modules/SitePermissions.jsm", "browser/modules/test/browser/browser_SitePermissions.js", "browser/modules/test/unit/test_SitePermissions.js", "dom/interfaces/base/nsIRemoteBrowser.idl", "dom/xbl/nsXBLWindowKeyHandler.cpp", "dom/xbl/nsXBLWindowKeyHandler.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "b65525d75c01cd73197b457f930c6415f3bfafdf", "parents": ["814806beaaf8d82d9ff8d57543263d8ca2720d51"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Neil Deakin \u003cneil@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 380637, move reserved key checking into ContentUtils so that it can be shared with menu accesskey checks , r=felipe", "files": ["dom/base/nsContentUtils.cpp", "dom/base/nsContentUtils.h", "dom/xbl/nsXBLWindowKeyHandler.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3a4fbb2ae0221a9cf3986bc18a199d3ddfcdb4b7", "parents": ["b65525d75c01cd73197b457f930c6415f3bfafdf"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Neil Deakin \u003cneil@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1411705, check the pseudo char code in GetAccessKeyCandidates so that this check works in both keydown and keypress events, r=masayuki", "files": ["widget/WidgetEventImpl.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a1030875b7c8c7b33e49c91aefeacdacc4425724", "parents": ["3a4fbb2ae0221a9cf3986bc18a199d3ddfcdb4b7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Neil Deakin \u003cneil@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 380637, when an Alt+accesskey for a menubar menu is pressed, check if the user has blocked sites from overriding keyboard shortcuts, and don't send the event to the page if so. Add a similar check for the F10 key which focuses the menubar. An additional capturing keydown listener is added because the key needs to be blocked before content sees it. r=masayuki", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/permissions/browser_reservedkey.js", "layout/xul/nsMenuBarListener.cpp", "layout/xul/nsMenuBarListener.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a812659b1aa89c977b90ecd58b3e8bcb07080095", "parents": ["a1030875b7c8c7b33e49c91aefeacdacc4425724"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Michael Ratcliffe \u003cmratcliffe@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1415554 - Inspector to use prop-types and react-dom-factories r=gl\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 7NxFwgFLDAL", "files": ["devtools/client/inspector/animation/components/AnimationItem.js", "devtools/client/inspector/animation/components/AnimationList.js", "devtools/client/inspector/animation/components/App.js", "devtools/client/inspector/animation/components/NoAnimationPanel.js", "devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/components/BoxModel.js", "devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/components/BoxModelApp.js", "devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/components/BoxModelEditable.js", "devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/components/BoxModelInfo.js", "devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/components/BoxModelMain.js", "devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/components/BoxModelProperties.js", "devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/components/ComputedProperty.js", "devtools/client/inspector/boxmodel/types.js", "devtools/client/inspector/components/InspectorTabPanel.js", "devtools/client/inspector/extensions/components/ExtensionSidebar.js", "devtools/client/inspector/extensions/components/ObjectTreeView.js", "devtools/client/inspector/fl