l, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "8135": {"changesets": [{"author": "L10n Bumper Bot \u003crelease+l10nbumper@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "no bug - Bumping Firefox l10n changesets DONTBUILD r=release a=l10n-bump\n\nwo -\u003e default", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cb9fd022bf7b28135f55ffbfff7ea7dbed07605e", "parents": ["092ccc6335a529133a8412a8f1bf1cdda872c6a9"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Hommey \u003cmh+mozilla@glandium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1402283 - Fix non-Nightly build bustage. r+a=RyanVM", "files": ["memory/gtest/TestJemalloc.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "50d59c3a291b7144fae5cb68aa1fb6e1493636e5", "parents": ["cb9fd022bf7b28135f55ffbfff7ea7dbed07605e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ryan VanderMeulen \u003cryanvm@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Merge mozilla-central to beta. a=merge, l10n=me on a CLOSED TREE", "files": ["browser/locales/l10n-changesets.json"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null, null], "node": "95bb0fe925ede241a79413eb0ed078e0c9c5f901", "parents": ["6c6c0e855154324123b4667ae35218dfcac74498", "50d59c3a291b7144fae5cb68aa1fb6e1493636e5"], "tags": []}], "date": 1510351121, "git_changesets": [null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "8136": {"changesets": [{"author": "Ryan VanderMeulen \u003cryanvm@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1402283 - Fix typo. r+a=RyanVM", "files": ["memory/gtest/TestJemalloc.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c32f513af0f875fd36d8951d60e05ba00ee2e39f", "parents": ["50d59c3a291b7144fae5cb68aa1fb6e1493636e5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ryan VanderMeulen \u003cryanvm@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Merge mozilla-central to beta. a=merge, l10n=me on a CLOSED TREE", "files": [], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null, null], "node": "16526b29e53427eb16c4557ee374230a4a8074a6", "parents": ["95bb0fe925ede241a79413eb0ed078e0c9c5f901", "c32f513af0f875fd36d8951d60e05ba00ee2e39f"], "tags": []}], "date": 1510351682, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "8137": {"changesets": [{"author": "Ryan VanderMeulen \u003cryanvm@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset 2ed0ff57330d (bug 1411467) for test_interfaces bustage on Beta.", "files": ["modules/libpref/init/all.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "933f9cd9b3b9030399a11c19cb4e5117b29e2772", "parents": ["c32f513af0f875fd36d8951d60e05ba00ee2e39f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ryan VanderMeulen \u003cryanvm@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Merge mozilla-central to beta. a=merge, l10n=me on a CLOSED TREE", "files": [], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null, null], "node": "3b4ee8c0d3c61b91f00aa6d99f81e9d51117053e", "parents": ["16526b29e53427eb16c4557ee374230a4a8074a6", "933f9cd9b3b9030399a11c19cb4e5117b29e2772"], "tags": []}], "date": 1510353132, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "8138": {"changesets": [{"author": "D\u00e3o Gottwald \u003cdao@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1215335 - Remove unused notification-inner container. r=bgrins\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: Hpv9WhHBdbZ", "files": ["browser/components/translation/translation-infobar.xml", "toolkit/content/widgets/notification.xml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2302ac35732fe1b030bf97203cc52c580a07a474", "parents": ["aa46c2b0b80b61c8e1ba7ac3f15d1d3616ae9305"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Tolfsen \u003cato@sny.no\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1414401 - Enable geckodriver on Linux i686 r=ted,whimboo\n\nThis patch enables building of geckodriver in CI on Linux i686.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: GkdHDJrzh2X", "files": ["toolkit/moz.configure"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "34708561a45cb9eded4866fa3ca1f1101e6f7c81", "parents": ["2302ac35732fe1b030bf97203cc52c580a07a474"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andreas Tolfsen \u003cato@sny.no\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1414401 - Schedule Wd tests on linux32 r=jgraham\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FRpg35u0NWK", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/test/test-sets.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "331c5f0d914ed183b52e5dcee72f8f31281cdde0", "parents": ["34708561a45cb9eded4866fa3ca1f1101e6f7c81"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aki Sasaki \u003casasaki@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1415391 - move release indexes into index_builder('release'). r=dustin\n\nIn bug 1412690, Dustin noted that the scopes and routes don't belong at the worker level.\nTo deal with the release indexes, we now have a new `index_builder`. We also add the default\nrelease bbb scope in `build_buildbot_bridge_payload`.\n\nWe can and should still move the product info to attributes. I left that for another patch.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 4ZqvnY577S7", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/beetmover-cdns/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-bouncer-aliases/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-bouncer-sub/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-mark-as-shipped/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-uptake-monitoring/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-version-bump/kind.yml", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/beetmover_cdns.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/buildbot.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/task.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a6108f6cc6a1859b2d9dfb705baefc044ea4871a", "parents": ["331c5f0d914ed183b52e5dcee72f8f31281cdde0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aki Sasaki \u003casasaki@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1415391 - fix beetmover-cdns worker-type schema. r=dustin\n\nI think I copied this from source_test.py, but didn't need it.  This patch switches to `optionally_keyed_by` and `resolve_keyed_by`. This also fixes a bug where our next mozilla-beta Fennec beta would have used the dev beetmover pool instead of the production pool.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: IdLNmFzieMi", "files": ["taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/beetmover_cdns.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "136574f7a5e4a793a8306f020c9d4b15655e0d53", "parents": ["a6108f6cc6a1859b2d9dfb705baefc044ea4871a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aki Sasaki \u003casasaki@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1415391 - move bbb properties under worker: r=dustin\n\nPer review comments in bug 1412690, this patch moves the `properties` definition under `worker:`, and resolves the `tuxedo_server_url` in the buildbot-bridge `payload_builder`.\n\nThis addresses [1] and [2].\n\n[1] https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1412690#c52\n[2] https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1412690#c54\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: JFAWr9Dk0gc", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/release-bouncer-aliases/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-uptake-monitoring/kind.yml", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/buildbot.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/task.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0fd32f2a273f58413d3c1a9d53125208e9d1d201", "parents": ["136574f7a5e4a793a8306f020c9d4b15655e0d53"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aki Sasaki \u003casasaki@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1415391 - parameterize next_version and build_number. r=dustin\n\nInstead of relying on environment variables, pass these in as parameters.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: An58Bu2kd1g", "files": ["taskcluster/docs/parameters.rst", "taskcluster/taskgraph/actions/release_promotion.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/decision.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/parameters.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/util/scriptworker.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "598578e14b9f833fbf3b27926fad0c1131b49304", "parents": ["0fd32f2a273f58413d3c1a9d53125208e9d1d201"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aki Sasaki \u003casasaki@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "bug 1415391 - add `shipping_phase` and `shipping_product` attributes. r=dustin\n\nThese two new attributes will help us determine which tasks belong in which release promotion graphs. In the future, we'll specify these for all shippable builds as well, and we can reduce the usage of the `product` keys. However, sometimes we need `product` to differ from `shipping-product` (e.g., `mobile` vs `fennec`; in this case we mean `stage_product` vs `shipping_product`), so I haven't yet touched those key/value pairs.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: LEuf4CS277Q", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/beetmover-cdns/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/push-apk-breakpoint/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/push-apk/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-bouncer-aliases/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-bouncer-sub/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-mark-as-shipped/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-notify-promote/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-notify-publish/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-uptake-monitoring/kind.yml", "taskcluster/ci/release-version-bump/kind.yml", "taskcluster/docs/attributes.rst", "taskcluster/taskgraph/target_tasks.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/beetmover_cdns.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/__init__.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/push_apk.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/push_apk_breakpoint.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/release_deps.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/task.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7d4154fe9a2644eee6302c6faf3a5d2c59b784a7", "parents": ["598578e14b9f833fbf3b27926fad0c1131b49304"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Sebastian Hengst \u003carchaeopteryx@coole-files.de\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Backed out changeset 2302ac35732f (bug 1215335) for notifi