9365 - Disable accessible/tests/mochitest/tree/test_tabbrowser.xul on linux debug for frequent failures. a=test-only", "files": ["accessible/tests/mochitest/tree/a11y.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "aba8957eb55bba88a8a8c441b2e64c9694ef67e5", "parents": ["653027753416d824f75dd5d5a24370c6a59b0d29"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Joel Maher \u003cjmaher@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1394967 - Disable browser_screenshots_ui_check.js on windows debug for frequent failures. a=test-only", "files": ["browser/extensions/screenshots/test/browser/browser.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a1622fcd6b42a3dda12d968043b22d02c6caf806", "parents": ["aba8957eb55bba88a8a8c441b2e64c9694ef67e5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Geoff Brown \u003cgbrown@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1365177 - Disable (random-if) reftest w3c-css/submitted/masking/mask-image-1c.html on linux for frequent intermittent failures. a=test-only", "files": ["layout/reftests/w3c-css/submitted/masking/reftest.list"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7dc24d06eb1f2354cf9fb9f7eb04d30dcf98f9ee", "parents": ["a1622fcd6b42a3dda12d968043b22d02c6caf806"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Geoff Brown \u003cgbrown@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1381451 - Disable browser-chrome test browser_819510_perwindowpb.js on linux for frequent intermittent failures. a=test-only", "files": ["browser/components/sessionstore/test/browser.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4f142cdbb0892b65bda5362b82cfc9c76ee11506", "parents": ["7dc24d06eb1f2354cf9fb9f7eb04d30dcf98f9ee"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Geoff Brown \u003cgbrown@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1294873 - Skip test_websocket-server.html on osx, to avoid intermittent leaks. a=test-only", "files": ["devtools/server/tests/mochitest/chrome.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f9062797bdb1c685df4294d10538f0377334594e", "parents": ["4f142cdbb0892b65bda5362b82cfc9c76ee11506"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nathaniel Nebel \u003cme@nathanielnebel.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1381459 - Allow closing of browserless tabs. r=whimboo, a=test-only\n\nClosing a tab should always be allowed, even if the current content browser doesn't exist.\nThis can be the case when a tab gets moved to a different process.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: LaU9MgEyCOx", "files": ["testing/marionette/driver.js", "testing/marionette/harness/marionette_harness/tests/unit/test_window_close_content.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5ae4d403609683591f541063742fbd0998f8fee1", "parents": ["f9062797bdb1c685df4294d10538f0377334594e"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Bob Silverberg \u003cbsilverberg@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1416039 - Fix intermittent browser_ext_tabs_lastAccessed.js. r=mixedpuppy, a=test-only\n\nThe recent failures all seem to be on the assertion that lastAccessed of tab 1 is\nlater than the test start time. It's possible that things happen so quickly that\nlastAccessed of tab 1 is the same as the start time, so this patch changes the\ncomparison to be a \u003c=.\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: 67CVQPj1ShM", "files": ["browser/components/extensions/test/browser/browser_ext_tabs_lastAccessed.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "99ad3a0eee48e6f2ed8544f9c07ec267a8b2f688", "parents": ["5ae4d403609683591f541063742fbd0998f8fee1"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Geoff Brown \u003cgbrown@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1418406 - Switch skip-if to fuzzy-if for Android select-disabled-fieldset-1.html and select-disabled-fieldset-2.html. a=test-only", "files": ["layout/reftests/css-invalid/select/reftest.list"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "480953f8ac70b0fcefee73f5c201e87d4ad98d74", "parents": ["99ad3a0eee48e6f2ed8544f9c07ec267a8b2f688"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aaron Klotz \u003caklotz@mozilla.com\u003e", "bra