b2f48824f8e795a4c39659b1ef43b"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Andrea Marchesini \u003camarchesini@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1421176 - nsMultiplexInputStream::Available() sanitize. r=smaug, a=gchang\n\n1. nsMultiplexInputStream::Available() should not return CLOSED if one of the\n   streams returns this error value. Instead it must check the following\n   streams.\n2. If a substream is async, available() should not check following streams\n   until that is closed.", "files": ["xpcom/io/nsMultiplexInputStream.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "52b742260c8458ebc7b0596e6e228cbb279332ab", "parents": ["0509c78748016f4e861affa165e4f510e540c692"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Henri Sivonen \u003chsivonen@hsivonen.fi\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1409951 - Use a stack to end serializer contexts instead of recomputing them. r=smaug, a=gchang\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: FOd8AUmtYyA", "files": ["dom/base/nsDocumentEncoder.cpp", "dom/base/nsPlainTextSerializer.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4fdfde11bc65377efc7668d38639e12ca338be17", "parents": ["52b742260c8458ebc7b0596e6e228cbb279332ab"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Alex Chronopoulos \u003cachronop@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1406772 - Get channel count from MSG. r=padenot, a=gchang", "files": ["dom/media/MediaStreamGraph.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ff143543997be6ade6aa526ace6a0bc18359e0eb", "parents": ["4fdfde11bc65377efc7668d38639e12ca338be17"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan-Ivar Bruaroey \u003cjib@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1422389 - Limit default engine resolution. r=mchiang, a=abillings\n\nMozReview-Commit-ID: LS1z7I4myeb", "files": ["dom/media/webrtc/MediaEngineDefault.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9d5bd4981da9467e86b7d512a4c0c82678b53c54", "parents": ["ff143543997be6ade6aa526ace6a0bc18359e0eb"], "tags": []}], "date": 1512592032, "git_changesets":